{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"22c3655a17","title":"右派言论——反对农业及工商业社会主义改造","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4af2721d17","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"22c3655a17"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"},{"id":"5841b1c66b","name":"上海财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1837b8b9d6","type":"title","text":"右派言论——反对农业及工商业社会主义改造","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"4aef81a94c","type":"authors","text":"上海财经学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"bf1008dfe0","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“中国农民苦”，“农业中矛盾是由于党领导产生”，“南斯拉夫的农业公社制度比中国合作社制度好”。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"9286b85cee","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“农民生活水平没有绝对提高，而是把贫富悬殊的情况拉平了。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"38c4550d88","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“我也要为农民呼吁，农民生活苦了，我们那里就是这样。过去坐小包车吃鱼肉的，现在还是照样坐小包车，吃大块肉；过去吃不上肉的，现在还是吃不上肉。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"2c73098069","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“农民一年辛苦到头，还是吃不上肉，他们没有钱，叫他们怎么能吃肉呢？”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"ce95c997a4","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)“生活提高的是党员和干部，中农、上中农和灾区农民生活下降了，我搞过农村工作，情况很了解。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"56ea791d96","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)“我们那里合作社搞得很糟，没有吃的，派下去的干部水平低，又没有文化。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"33b2752ebe","type":"paragraph","text":"(7)“我们学习的是合作化好的方面，实际上是合作化一塌糊涂，干部贪污，强迫农民入社，不许农民退社，农民收入减少。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"eb0897339a","type":"paragraph","text":"(8)“农民太苦，一年只有120元，而工人工资拿了很多。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"ae274a832b","type":"paragraph","text":"(9)“中国人民生活水平与苏联相差很多，特别落后于美国好多倍，最糟最苦的是农民。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"511d29b85c","type":"paragraph","text":"(10)“合作化了，没出现生产高潮，而是低潮。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"085b8c7f53","type":"paragraph","text":"(11)“开放自由市场后，有的地方出现了少数社员不参加集体劳动，而去跑小市场，这说明合作社不好，要不然为什么农民不喜欢合作社而赶市集去呢？”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"7c6fd0d990","type":"paragraph","text":"(12)“无产阶级专政是对资产阶级专政，而农业合作化对农民也是进行专政。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"b6bdb54e55","type":"paragraph","text":"(13)“农村一团糟，合作化问题多。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"231e74fd13","type":"paragraph","text":"(14)“合作化有大缺点：财务管理差，干部水平低，劳动调配差，社内民主差。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"892f70013b","type":"paragraph","text":"(15)“农民加入合作社是强迫的。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"1c41223ffb","type":"paragraph","text":"(16)“农业合作化忽左忽右。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"15497ff52a","type":"paragraph","text":"(17)“合作社只是喂肥了干部。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"ba6e0c0e17","type":"paragraph","text":"(18)“我不同意周总理报告中说：‘人民生活有提高’，我认为不应该讲大道理，应具体分析，我农乡农民谷子卖给政府是一角一斤，农民向国家买一元三斤。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"be371b907b","type":"subtitle","text":"反对资本主义工商业社会主义改造","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"060cbbd518","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“我父亲是劳动起家，既是劳动者，又是剥削者，有二重性。”","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"0e1d4ef113","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“资本家经过三反、五反、抗美援朝等一系列运动后，觉悟都有一定程度的提高，还要求脱胎换骨，似乎有些刁难资本家。”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"},{"id":"7d4da87ab9","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《反右派斗争言论选辑　第一辑　学生部份》（中共上海财经学院委员会编，1957年9","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17"}],"page":{"id":"501f727b6f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"22c3655a17","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}